headline: 5 Tech Gifts This Mom Influencer Says Are on Her List — and Should Be on Yours Too
summary: BELLEVUE, Wash., November 25, 2024--To her nearly 1 million followers, Kendall Mariah is known as a mom with big southern charm and big-time family finds for any occasion. The holidays are especially her time to shine with recommendations for parents and families who appreciate her genuine reviews and practical advice.
